	.container
		.row
			.col-lg-9
				h3 Why

				p This is a free API. Postcodes.io is aimed at developers who want a resource to lookup and (reverse) geocode UK Postcodes.

				h3 Community API Libraries

				p
					strong PHP
				p
					a(href="https://github.com/boxuk/postcodes-io-bundle") postcodes-io-bundle 
					| by the people at 
					a(href="http://www.boxuk.com") Box UK
					| . Read the 
					a(href="http://www.boxuk.com/developer-blog/geocoding-postcodes-symfony2/") blog post.
					br
					a(href="https://github.com/adityamenon/postcodes-io-laravel") postcodes-io laravel package 
					| by 
					a(href="http://adityamenon.co") Aditya Menon
					| .

				p 
					strong Ruby 
				p 
					a(href="https://github.com/jamesruston/postcodes_io") postcodes_io 
					| by 
					a(href="https://github.com/jamesruston") James Ruston

				h3 Noticeboard for 2014

				p Any updates or disruptions will be listed below.

				ul
					li 13 Dec. Disruption 14:00-1420 GMT. A number of API methods were returning 500s due to a bad build. Now fixed.
					li 11 Dec. Updated Database. Database now based on November 2014 release of ONSPD's Postcode Directory. 
					li 18 Oct. Updated Database. Database now based on August 2014 release of ONSPD's Postcode Directory. 
					li 7 Oct. Geocoding disruption. Some geocoding API methods were returning incorrect results after a scheduled update. Now fixed.
					li 5 Oct. New installation instructions. We've begun hosting a pg_dump of our database for rapid self deployment. See Github &amp; Documentation for more information.
					li 16 Sep. Added nearest postcode method. Get nearest postcodes for given postcode.
					li 15 Jun. Updated Database. Database now based on May 2014 release of ONSPD's Postcode Directory.
					li 16 Apr. Added Clinical Commission Group Data.

