				h3 Github
				p For bugs, feature requests and spelling corrections use our 
					a(href="https://github.com/ideal-postcodes/postcodes.io/issues") Github issue tracker.

				h3 Data

				p This API is up-to-date with the ONS' Postcode Directory for November 2014. Beyond that date, new postcodes may be added. Existing postcodes may be amended or discontinued. This information will not be captured until the next quarterly update.

